{"tid":246918,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"東華又想整爆物理治療physiotherapy","createTime":"2017-05-17T11:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T04:23:14.000Z","uid":71374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e90a87e2d49289bcf5d12fbce2668ddb068f0a7","tid":246918,"uid":71374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T11:35:50.000Z","msg":"東華學院盈餘逾百萬擬遷新址 <span style=\"color: red;\">5年後申請升格大學</span><br />\n<br />\n「指定專業/界別課程資助計劃」（SSSDP）恆常化，名額由原來1,000個增加至3,000個，資助學生修讀自資院校的指定專業範疇課程。東華學院校長呂汝漢表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">該校現有3個課程包括護理、放射治療及醫療化驗科學學士課程</span>，共有232個學額已獲SSSDP資助，下一步會申請將餘下38個自資學資額納入計劃，另他預料職業治療學士課程於今年第二季可獲最終審批（ full accreditation），希望該課程50個學額亦能納入SSSDP計劃。<br />\n<br />\n呂汝漢又公佈<span style=\"color: red;\">未來5年發展計劃，包括積極開辦新課程</span>，醫療相關學科包括<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">物理治療學士</span></span></span></span>、食物安全等學士課程，計劃未來1、2年開辦，另會擴展非醫療學科課程，例如幼兒教育、工商管理及心理輔導等，為5年後申請升格成為私立大學鋪路。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，現有校舍空間不足，<span style=\"color: red;\">未來5年須物色附加校舍</span>，學院近年財政趨穩健，近伴錄得200至300萬盈餘，相信有能力應付新校舍開支。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56317078&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170217\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56317078%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170217&d=Ur8nmiChwnCvVlPnSGk5XqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=a8f03f72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56317078%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170217&h=0a0102d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56317078&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170217</a>"},{"pid":"47131fa5238a42d27572dc610e5053a10ca53479","tid":246918,"uid":71374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited